  ibadan ( or fully ( ìlú ) ẹ̀bá-ọ̀dàn , ( the city at ) the edge of the savannah ) is the capital city of oyo state and the third largest metropolitan area , by population , in nigeria , after lagos and kano , with a population of over 3 million , and the largest metropolitan geographical area .

